channel.title: Diff'rent Strokes with Jade & Dave
channel.description:
Diff'rent Strokes is a radio program that celebrates diversity with the comedic meshing of polar opposite co hosts Jade and Dave.
The show can be heard live Wednesday nights 1opm- 11pm on JOY 94.9, a GLBTI radio station in Melbourne, Australia.
